divs: Sighting Detailsarived at job site about 9.20 am cdt, nobody on job. started looking around and then looked southeast in sky and noticed a silver object, looked like a ballon at first bright silver and shining. so I wanted to watch the object to see how it would float. then the object looked like some thing was hanking down from it still silver, I thought it was about 2-3000 feet high, and then its became a long and wide cigar shaped object that was white with to very stubby wings one on each side each wing was about 25% the lenght of the object the object, the obcect had no tail section at all, and it knowed looked like it was at about 10000 feet or higher and moving in a northwesterly direction at higher then normal speed compared to a jet . I lost sight of the object after about 3-5 min. after I first spoted it. Also the object looked to be a transparent white and I thought that was odd. the body of the object apeared to look wider than a jet. it was not a jet.
Summary: silver then turning white, very long with two very short wings 2/3 back for the nose of the craft
